data.description: Do not miss this lovely 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom 1.5 story home in the Skyline Village neighborhood, with two-story cathedral ceiling in the living/entry. Built in 1988, this contemporary style home feels like-new with remodel completed in 2024 including carpet, paint, butcher block countertops, and more! You will love the covered back patio for relaxing, entertaining, and enjoying the up-close view of the Hogbacks from the privacy fenced back yard with xeriscaping, mature cottonwoods, and large storage shed. Forced air gas heat, and central air-conditioning make this home comfortable year round with an open, sunny feel throughout. Attached 2-car garage, RV parking and all kitchen appliances included. Nothing to do here but move right in and make this home your own!
